---
title: DIY Butter Chicken with Basmati Rice and Peas
description: Takeout, fakeout! Our lighter version of butter chicken is going to be your new favourite recipe. Marinated Indian-spiced chicken sits atop fragrant veggie rice finished with a sprinkle of cilantro leaves for a dish that's as comforting as it is beautiful.
